data.description: *Assumable VA Loan 3.375% APR which is huge! Waterfront  Penthouse located right on the Bay with views of Bay and Ocean.  This spacious one bedroom, penthouse is currently undergoing extensive  renovations to the kitchen, bathroom, closets, floors and Walls, utilizing quality materials and finishes.  This is a very sought after luxury building with top-notch amenities, including an incredible gym with views of the bay and pool, a recreation room with all the bells and whistles, Conference room set up with a computer and monitor and pool deck with jacuzzi and BBQ.  The location  is phenomenal.
